Quickstrike:




Quickstrike crawled forward, then turned his long body to the side, trying 
to grasp the blanket on his back. The spun around once, looking as if he was 
chasing his tail.

"Yeah," he said to Dar Mouse. "Get this dang blanket offa me." He had it 
covering the entire hood and head of his tail. He couldn't grab the edges, 
due that the fact that he had his tail too high up.
